    • Constructor Detail

      • StackCameraDeviceSimulator

        public StackCameraDeviceSimulator(java.lang.String pDeviceName,
                                  Variable<java.lang.Boolean> pTriggerVariable)
        Crates a Stack Camera Device Simulator of a given name. Stacks from a default noisy stack provider are sent to the output variable when a positive edge is sent to the trigger variable (false -> true). the stack provider can be changed at any point if needed.
        Parameters:
        pDeviceName - camera device name
        pTriggerVariable - trigger variable

      • StackCameraDeviceSimulator

        public StackCameraDeviceSimulator(java.lang.String pDeviceName,
                                  StackCameraSimulationProvider pStackCameraSimulationProvider,
                                  Variable<java.lang.Boolean> pTriggerVariable)
        Crates a StackCameraDeviceSimulator of a given name. Stacks from the given stack provider are sent to the output variable when a positive edge is sent to the trigger variable (false -> true).
        Parameters:
        pDeviceName - camera device name
        pStackCameraSimulationProvider - stack provider
        pTriggerVariable - trigger variable
